Alembic migrations for the FastAPI Kanban service.

The migration environment reads the database URL from APP_POSTGRESQL_DSN. If the
environment variable is not set, it falls back to AppSettings().postgresql_dsn.

Apply migrations:

    uv run alembic upgrade head

Create a migration after updating SQLModel table definitions:

    uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"

See ../docs/operations.md for deployment and rollback notes.
